This folder has a variety of scripts to demonstrate how to created supercells and defect structures for MgO.

Input_Files:
------------
MgO_NaCl_unit.vasp - a unit cell structure of MgO in rocksalt.

Scripts:
--------
poscar_make_MgO_333.py - makes a 3x3x3 supercell of rocksalt MgO
poscar_make_MgO_333_fr_a.py - makes a 3x3x3 supercell of rocksalt MgO with an
	oxygen Frenkel defect.
poscar_make_MgO_333_fr_c.py - makes a 3x3x3 supercell of rocksalt MgO with an
        magnesium Frenkel defect
poscar_make_MgO_333_sch.py - makes a 3x3x3 supercell of rocksalt MgO with an
        Schottky defect.
poscar_make_MgO_001_s.py - makes a rocksalt MgO slab with [001] surface

Generated Output Files:
-----------------------
poscar_make_MgO_333.py      -> MgO_NaCl_333.vasp
poscar_make_MgO_333_fr_a.py -> MgO_NaCl_333_fr_a.vasp
poscar_make_MgO_333_fr_c.py -> MgO_NaCl_333_fr_c.vasp
poscar_make_MgO_333_sch.py  -> MgO_NaCl_333_sch.vasp
poscar_make_MgO_001_s.py    -> MgO_NaCl_001_s.vasp
